title: Pawn Stars S08E77 Chumdae HDTV H.264 720.avi
description:
Pawn Stars
S08E77 	"Chumdae" 	July 17, 2014

Rev your engines with the Pawn Stars when a legendary 1967 Shelby GT350 speeds into the shop. 
Will Rick be able to cruise through the negotiation or will it be gone in 60 seconds? Then, Corey 
and Chumlee play with the idea of buying one of the first video game consoles, a Magnavox Odyssey 200. 
Can they figure out how to beat the system or will it be game over? And later, Chumlee seeks the go ahead 
from Rick to test out the shop's new ice cream maker. Will the guys all scream for ice cream or will Rick
give Chumlee the cold shoulder?
